<h4 id="任务列表的多层嵌套"><a href="#任务列表的多层嵌套" class="headerlink" title="任务列表的多层嵌套"></a>任务列表的多层嵌套</h4><p><strong>代码：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [ ] 总任务1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">	-</span> [ ] 未完成任务</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">	-</span> [x] 已完成任务项	</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [ ] 总任务2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">	-</span> [ ] 未完成任务</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">	-</span> [x] 已完成任务项	</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

